nam yajamanru ( kannada : ನಂಯಜಮಾನ ರು ) is a 2009 indian kannada drama film directed and written by t. s. nagabharana . the film stars vishnuvardhan along with lakshmi gopalaswamy , navya nair and vijay raghavendra in the lead roles . the film was produced by rajakumari rajshekar . the film released on 27 february 2009 to generally positive reviews from critics . however , the film failed commercially at the box-office .